#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:1
msgid "eHealth"
msgstr "eHealth"

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:4
msgid ""
"MDA insurability, eFact electronic invoicing and eAgreement agreements in "
"Resthome."
msgstr ""
"Verzekerbaarheid MDA, elektronische facturatie eFact en akkoorden eAgreement"
" in Resthome."

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:7
msgid ""
"Resthome is connected to the Belgian e-health ecosystem (eHealth, MyCareNet,"
" WalCareNet) to exchange directly with the mutualities."
msgstr ""
"Resthome is verbonden met het Belgische e-gezondheidsecosysteem (eHealth, "
"MyCareNet, WalCareNet) om rechtstreeks met de mutualiteiten uit te wisselen."

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:10
msgid "The services"
msgstr "De diensten"

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:12
msgid "**MDA — Insurability**"
msgstr "**MDA — Verzekerbaarheid**"

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:14
msgid ""
"Checks that a resident is **insured** and retrieves their mutuality and BIM "
"status, individually or in batch."
msgstr ""
"Controleert of een bewoner **verzekerd** is en haalt zijn mutualiteit en "
"BIM-status op, individueel of in batch."

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:17
msgid "→ [Insurability in detail](mda.md)"
msgstr "→ [De verzekerbaarheid in detail](mda.md)"

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:19
msgid "**eFact — Electronic invoicing**"
msgstr "**eFact — Elektronische facturatie**"

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:21
msgid ""
"Sends the **mutuality share** (message 920000) to the insurance "
"organisations and follows the acknowledgements and settlements."
msgstr ""
"Verstuurt het **mutualiteitsaandeel** (bericht 920000) naar de "
"verzekeringsinstellingen en volgt de ontvangstbewijzen en afrekeningen op."

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:24
msgid "→ [eFact invoicing in detail](efact.md)"
msgstr "→ [De eFact-facturatie in detail](efact.md)"

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:26
msgid "**eAgreement — Agreements**"
msgstr "**eAgreement — Akkoorden**"

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:28
msgid ""
"Notifies the OA on an **admission**, an **end of stay** or an **absence** "
"(Annexes 7, 10, 11…)."
msgstr ""
"Meldt de VI bij een **opname**, een **einde verblijf** of een "
"**afwezigheid** (Bijlagen 7, 10, 11…)."

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:31
msgid "→ [Agreements in detail](eagreement.md)"
msgstr "→ [De akkoorden in detail](eagreement.md)"

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:33
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "Vereisten"

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:35
msgid "To check before sending"
msgstr "Te controleren vóór het versturen"

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:37
msgid "The resident has a valid **NISS**."
msgstr "De bewoner heeft een geldig **NISS**."

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:38
msgid "Their **mutuality** is filled in."
msgstr "Zijn **mutualiteit** is ingevuld."

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:39
msgid "An **insurability (MDA)** has been checked for the period."
msgstr "Er is een **verzekerbaarheid (MDA)** gecontroleerd voor de periode."

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:40
msgid "The establishment's **eHealth certificate** is active."
msgstr "Het **eHealth-certificaat** van de instelling is actief."

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:43
msgid "Good to know"
msgstr "Goed om te weten"

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:45
msgid ""
"An **absence** of more than 72 h (or any hospitalisation) triggers an end-"
"of-accommodation **Annexe 11**; the **return** generates a readmission "
"**Annexe 7**."
msgstr ""
"Een **afwezigheid** van meer dan 72 u (of elke hospitalisatie) lokt een "
"**Bijlage 11** einde verblijf uit; de **terugkeer** genereert een **Bijlage "
"7** heropname."

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:48
msgid ""
"An invoice that is already **posted** \"freezes\" the month's billing for "
"that resident: to change it, reset it to draft (or issue a credit note), "
"then refresh."
msgstr ""
"Een reeds **geboekte** factuur « bevriest » de facturatie van de maand voor "
"die bewoner: om ze te wijzigen, zet ze terug naar concept (of maak een "
"creditnota op) en vernieuw dan."

#: ../../content/ehealth/index.md:52
msgid "What's next"
msgstr "Verder"

